THE GAME
--------

  'HipBarr' is a Workbench game where you have to move a coloured
diagonal bar that spans two tiles, so a part of it gets to the
'exit' tile, which is located at the lower right of the game
board. To complicate matters, other diagonal bars are placed here
and there on the board to block the way, so you also have to move
those bars in order to get to the exit...

  If you get stuck on a game board, you can click on the 'Replay'
button to start over, but be aware that the amount of moves you
make for the current game board is added up until you complete
it...

  Complete each game board in the least amount of moves.

  Have fun!

